<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>üö® Alerte Erreur - {{ project.name }} - Error Explorer</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .alert-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .email-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .email-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .error-summary {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .error-meta {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .meta-item {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6;
        }

        .meta-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .meta-value {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .stack-trace {
            background: #1e293b;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            overflow-x: auto;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #64748b;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .priority-high {
            border-left-color: #ef4444;
        }

        .priority-medium {
            border-left-color: #f59e0b;
        }

        .priority-low {
            border-left-color: #10b981;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background: #1e293b;
            color: #94a3b8;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer-text {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #60a5fa;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .unsubscribe {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .unsubscribe a {
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .email-header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .email-body {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .email-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .error-meta {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }

            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .footer-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
        <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-text">Error Explorer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert-badge">
            {% if errorGroup.httpStatusCode >= 500 %}
                üö® ALERTE CRITIQUE
            {% elseif errorGroup.occurrenceCount > 10 %}
                ‚ö†Ô∏è ALERTE √âLEV√âE
            {% else %}
                üî¥ NOUVELLE ERREUR
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h1 class="email-title">Erreur d√©tect√©e</h1>
        <p class="email-subtitle">{{ project.name }} - {{ errorGroup.environment ?: 'Production' }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
        <div class="section">
            <div class="error-summary">
                <div class="error-title">{{ errorGroup.exceptionClass }}</div>
                <div class="error-message">{{ errorGroup.message }}</div>
                
                <div class="error-meta">
                    <div class="meta-item priority-{% if errorGroup.httpStatusCode >= 500 %}high{% elseif errorGroup.occurrenceCount > 5 %}medium{% else %}low{% endif %}">
                        <div class="meta-label">Occurrences</div>
                        <div class="meta-value">{{ errorGroup.occurrenceCount }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <div class="meta-label">Premi√®re fois</div>
                        <div class="meta-value">{{ errorGroup.firstSeen|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <div class="meta-label">Derni√®re fois</div>
                        <div class="meta-value">{{ errorGroup.lastSeen|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</div>
                    </div>
                    {% if errorGroup.httpStatusCode %}
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <div class="meta-label">Code HTTP</div>
                        <div class="meta-value">{{ errorGroup.httpStatusCode }}</div>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Localisation</h2>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <div class="meta-label">Fichier</div>
                <div class="meta-value">{{ errorGroup.file }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div class="meta-label">Ligne</div>
                <div class="meta-value">{{ errorGroup.line }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {% if errorGroup.stackTracePreview %}
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Aper√ßu de la Stack Trace</h2>
            <div class="stack-trace">{{ errorGroup.stackTracePreview|slice(0, 500) }}{% if errorGroup.stackTracePreview|length > 500 %}...{% endif %}</div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="{{ dashboardUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary">
                üîç Voir les d√©tails
            </a>
            <a href="{{ dashboardUrl }}" class="btn btn-secondary">
                ‚úÖ Marquer comme r√©solu
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Actions recommand√©es</h2>
            <ul style="padding-left: 20px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.8;">
                {% if errorGroup.httpStatusCode >= 500 %}
                <li>üö® <strong>Priorit√© √©lev√©e</strong> - Erreur serveur critique affectant les utilisateurs</li>
                <li>üîç V√©rifiez les logs serveur pour plus de contexte</li>
                {% endif %}
                {% if errorGroup.occurrenceCount > 5 %}
                <li>üìä Cette erreur se r√©p√®te fr√©quemment ({{ errorGroup.occurrenceCount }} fois)</li>
                {% endif %}
                <li>üîß Examinez le code autour de la ligne {{ errorGroup.line }} dans {{ errorGroup.file|split('/')|last }}</li>
                <li>üìù Consultez la documentation pour {{ errorGroup.exceptionClass }}</li>
                <li>‚úÖ Marquez comme r√©solue une fois corrig√©e</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
        <div class="footer-text">
            <strong>Error Explorer</strong><br>
            Monitoring d'erreurs en temps r√©el pour {{ project.name }}
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="{{ dashboardUrl }}" class="footer-link">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="{{ dashboardUrl }}" class="footer-link">Projet {{ project.name }}</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="unsubscribe">
            <a href="{{ unsubscribeUrl }}">Se d√©sabonner des alertes</a> | 
            <a href="{{ dashboardUrl }}">G√©rer les notifications</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>